<script>
document.addEventListener('copy', function(event) {
    var now = new Date();
    var event_date = now.toISOString().split('T')[0];
    var event_time = now.toTimeString().split(' ')[0];
    var copiedText = window.getSelection().toString();
    if (copiedText.trim() !== '') {
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        window.dataLayer.push({
          event: 'text_copied',
          event_activity: 'Copying Text On Page',
          event_date: event_date,
          event_time: event_time,
          copied_text: copiedText
        });
        alert("টেক্সট কপি করা হয়েছে।");
    }
});
</script>

<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
      var submitBtn = document.getElementById('submitButton');
  
      if (submitBtn) {
        alert('Submit button পাওয়া গেছে');
        console.log('Submit button পাওয়া গেছে');
  
        submitBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
          var textValue = '';
          var input = document.getElementById('textInputBox');
  
          if (input) {
            alert('Input box পাওয়া গেছে');
            console.log('Input box পাওয়া গেছে');
            textValue = input.value;
          }
  
          window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
          alert('DataLayer প্রস্তুত');
          console.log('DataLayer প্রস্তুত');
  
          window.dataLayer.push({
            event: 'demoCustomEvent',
            textBoxData: textValue
          });
  
          alert('DataLayer-এ তথ্য পাঠানো হয়েছে: ' + textValue);
          console.log('DataLayer-এ তথ্য পাঠানো হয়েছে:', textValue);
        });
      }
    });
  </script>

<script>
  var now = new Date();
  var event_date = now.toISOString().split('T')[0];
